---
import FeatureCard from "../components/FeatureCard.astro";
---

<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 lg:flex-row pb-4 lg:px-layout-lg md:px-layout-md sm:px-layout-sm px-layout mt-10">
        <FeatureCard name="pillar-1" title="Multi-Modal Fusion">
            Synthesising complementary information from medical imaging
            (MICCAI/ISBI) and clinical records. I develop fusion architectures
            that robustly integrate diverse data modalities.
        </FeatureCard>
        <div class="grow" />
        <FeatureCard name="pillar-2" title="Uncertainty Quantification">
            Designing deep learning frameworks that rigorously quantify
            uncertainty. My work ensures AI systems are aware of their own
            limitations, crucial for safe clinical deployment.
        </FeatureCard>
        <div class="grow" />
        <FeatureCard name="pillar-3" title="Medical Foundation Models"
            >Adapting state-of-the-art Large Language Models (LLMs) for
            healthcare. I focus on fine-tuning foundation models to be both
            explainable and clinically accurate.
        </FeatureCard>
    </div>